Based on the `reaction` library structure, `reaction::Resource<T>` conditionally inherits from `reaction::memory::SBOResource<T>` or a heap-based resource depending on `reaction::memory::SBOTraits<T>::is_sbo_eligible`. Therefore, we can query the SBO state by checking this trait.

